---
title: Ultimate BBQ Pack | Serves 4 with Beef Cheeseburger, Pork Sausage & Chicken
description: There’s no better way to enjoy the summer than with friends and family by the barbeque. Gather your mates, fire up the barbie and
enjoy this delicious feast! For meat lovers, take a big bite out of a hearty cheeseburger, grilled to smokey perfection alongside herbed
pork sausages and succulent chicken thigh. To complete this pack, we’ve got you covered with an array of grilled and fresh sides like
haloumi, courgette and a refreshing leafy salad. The best thing about this pack is you can customise it your way. Go for your life!
